<view>
  <view id="header" style="height:100vh">
    <view id="logo">
      <image class="logo" src="/images/include/head_white.png" alt=""></image>
    </view>
    <view id="banner">
      <view class="content">
        <text>葡萄酒按月订购 </text>
        <text>像订阅杂志一样订阅红酒</text>
        <text>199元两瓶/月起 </text>
        <view class="icon">
          <image class="img" src="/images/home/icon.png" alt=""></image>
        </view>
        <view class="desc">
          <text>品质之选 </text>
          <text>每月给自己一个惊喜 </text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="other">
        <navigator class="subscribe" url="/pages/subscribe/subscribe">立即订阅</navigator>
        <image animation="{{animationData}}" class="next" src="/images/home/down.png"></image>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="first item">
    <view class="text">
      <view class="title-group">
        <text class="number"><i class="the"></i> FIRST</text>
        <text class="title">葡萄酒按月订购</text>
        <view class="line"></view>
        <text class="sub-title">MANNER</text>
      </view>
      <view class="desc">
        <text>每月甄选两款品质红酒 </text>
        <text>由国际权威侍酒师为您精心挑选 </text>
        <text>您可以订阅3个月、6个月或是一整年 </text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="image">
      <image src="/images/home/first.jpg" alt=""></image>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="second item">
    <view class="text">
      <view class="title-group">
        <text class="number"><i class="the"></i> SECOND</text>
        <text class="title">精选品质红酒</text>
        <view class="line"></view>
        <text class="sub-title">QUALITY</text>
      </view>
      <view class="desc">
        <text>以梦为马，诗酒趁年华</text>
        <text>层层筛选与进口商或酒庄直接合作</text>
        <text>所选酒款均为经得起检验的国际流通酒款</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="image">
      <image src="/images/home/second.jpg" alt=""></image>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="third item">
    <view class="text">
      <view class="title-group">
        <text class="number"><i class="the"></i> THIRD</text>
        <text class="title">从此爱上它</text>
        <view class="line"></view>
        <text class="sub-title">CULTURE</text>
      </view>
      <view class="desc">
        <text>和他/她亲密无间</text>
        <text>或是爱意浓浓</text>
        <text>曼妙时光，杯酒人生</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="image">
      <image src="/images/home/third.jpg" alt=""></image>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="fourth item">
    <view class="text">
      <view class="title-group">
        <text class="number"><i class="the"></i> FOURTH</text>
        <text class="title">订阅玩法</text>
        <view class="line"></view>
        <text class="sub-title">RULE</text>
      </view>
      <view class="desc">
        <text>每月5号为您准时寄出两款红酒佳酿</text>
        <text>新订阅用户可获得“酒零候”订阅礼包</text>
        <text>海马刀和《品酒手册》</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
